:: Test G Sample Storylet 6 [test] {"position":"1150,4900","size":"100,100"}
{=

(storylet: when
(passage:)'s name is "Test G"
and ($funcCheckExists: $char's player's quests, "urgentAssignment", "") is "failed"
and ($funcCheckExists: $char's player's timerQuest, "urgentAssignment", "") contains "deadline"
)
(exclusivity: 1)
(metadata: "title", "Berated", "cardDesc", "You've failed, so you have to hear all about it.", "img", "https://thefifthcity.wiki/w/images/3/3f/Currency3_copper.png",)

Your teacher berates you for not completing the essay on time. You try to give him what you have, but he's won't accept.
<br>
$cssDesc[This storylet should only appear once after you've failed the quest. The deadline timer is removed now, after the quest has failed, so that the storylet will not retrigger.]
<br>
---
(link-rerun: "Ugh.")[\
	(set: _reset to ($funcCheckExists: $char's player's att, "urgentAssignment", 0))\
	($funcGainLoss: "att.", "urgentAssignment", -_reset)\
    ($funcRemoveTimer: "urgentAssignment", "deadline")\
    (goto: "Test G")\
    ]<!--[[Test G]]-->